f Football History & Statistics |date=4 January 2016 |accessdate=26 May 2017}}</ref>\n*[[FIFPro World XI]]: [[FIFPro#Winners|2006]]<ref name=\"FIFPro World XI 2006\"/>\n*[[FIFPro#FIFA FIFPro World XI|FIFA FIFPro World XI]] 3rd team: 2013, 2014<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/news-and-comment/fifpro-announces-reserve-teams-of-the-year-but-luis-suarez-and-arjen-robben-wont-be-laughing-while-9062047.html#gallery |title=FifPro announces reserve Teams of the Year \u2013 but Luis Suarez and Arjen Robben won't be laughing while Iker Casillas is somehow named the second best goalkeeper of 2013 |newspaper=The Independent |date=15 January 2014 |accessdate=1 October 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fifpro.org/news/fifa-fifpro-world-xi-the-reserve-teams/en/ |title=FIFA FIFPro World XI: the reserve teams \u2013 FIFPro World Players' Union |publisher=FIFPro |date=15 January 2015 |accessdate=1 October 2017}}</ref>\n*[[Ballon d'Or]]: [[2006 Ballon d'Or|2006]] (9th place),<ref name=\"2006 Ballon d'Or\"/><ref name=\"2006 Ballon d'Or - RSSSF\">{{cite web |url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/europa-poy06.html |title=European Footballer of the Year (\"Ballon d'Or\") 2006 |publisher=Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation |author1=Jos\u00e9 Luis Pierrend |date=3 January 2007 |accessdate=8 November 2017}}</ref> [[2007 Ballon d'Or|2007]] (5th place),<ref name=\"2007 Ballon d'Or\"/> [[2012 FIFA Ballon d'Or|2012]] (7th place)<ref name=\"voting results\"/><ref name=\"2012 Pallone d'Oro FIFA\">{{cite news |url=http://www.repubblica.it/sport/calcio/esteri/2013/01/07/news/pallone_d_oro_messi_ronaldo_iniesta-50069574/ |title=Pallone d'Oro, Messi fa poker ed entra nella storia |newspaper=la Repubblica |language=Italian |author1=Luigi Panella |date=7 January 2013 |accessdate=8 November 2017}}</ref>\n*[[FIFA World Player of the Year]]: [[2007 FIFA World Player of the Year|2007]] (7th place)<ref name=\"FIFA Confederations Cup Brazil 2013 Player Profile: Andrea Pirlo\"/>\n*[[UEFA Super Cup]] Man of the Match: [[2007 UEFA Super Cup|2007]]<ref name=\"UEFA Super Cup Match Press Kit\"/>\n*[[ESPN]] World Team of the Decade: 2009<ref>{{cite news |last=Brewin |first=John |url=http://www.espnfc.com/story/717519/espn-soccernet-international-team-of-the-decade |title=World Team of the Decade |date=25 December 2009 |website=ESPN FC |accessdate=29 January 2018}}</ref>\n*[[European Sports Media#ESM Team of the Year|ESM Team of the Year]]: [[European Sports Media#2011\u201312|2011\u201312]]<ref name=el>{{cite web |url=http://www.elfvoetbal.nl/nieuws/188841_een-landgenoot-in-esm-elftal-van-het-seizoen |title=E\u00e9n landgenoot in ESM Elftal van het Seizoen |publisher=ElfVoetbal.nl |language=Dutch |accessdate=5 June 2012}}</ref>\n*[[Pallone d'Argento]]: 2011\u201312<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.airc.it/aiutare-la-ricerca/eventi/in-corso/locali/piemonte-valle-d-aosta/pallone-argento-pirlo/ |title=Pallone d'argento 2011\u201312 |publisher=Associazione Italiana per la Ricerca sul Cancro |language=Italian |date=13 May 2012 |accessdate=30 May 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Pallone Azzurro]]: 2012<ref>{{cite web |url=http://vivoazzurro.it/news/pirlo-e-il-pallone-azzurro-2012/ |title=Pirlo \u00e8 il Pallone Azzurro 2012 |publisher=Italian Football Federation |language=Italian |accessdate=6 February 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Guerin d'Oro]]: 2012<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/italpoy.html |title=Italy \u2013 Footballer of the Year |publisher=Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation |accessdate=6 February 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150121013030/http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/italpoy.html |archivedate=21 January 2015}}</ref>\n*[[UEFA European Championship Teams of the Tournament]]: [[UEFA Euro 2012#Awards|2012]]<ref name=\"UEFA: Andrea Pirlo\"/>\n*[[UEFA Best Player in Europe Award]]: [[UEFA Best Player in Europe Award#2011.E2.80.9312|2012]] (4th place),<ref name=\"UEFA: Andrea Pirlo\"/> [[UEFA Bes