ootballers]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Brescia Calcio players]]\n[[Category:Inter Milan players]]\n[[Category:Reggina 1914 players]]\n[[Category:A.C. Milan players]]\n[[Category:Juventus F.C. players]]\n[[Category:New York City FC players]]\n[[Category:Serie A players]]\n[[Category:Serie B players]]\n[[Category:Major League Soccer players]]\n[[Category:Designated Players (MLS)]]\n[[Category:Major League Soccer All-Stars]]\n[[Category:UEFA Champions League winning players]]\n[[Category:Association football players who received a testimonial]]\n[[Category:Italy under-21 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Olympic footballers of Italy]]\n[[Category:Italy international footballers]]\n[[Category:Footballers at the 2000 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:UEFA Euro 2004 players]]\n[[Category:Footballers at the 2004 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:2006 FIFA World Cup players]]\n[[Category:UEFA Euro 2008 players]]\n[[Category:2009 FIFA Confederations Cup players]]\n[[Category:2010 FIFA World Cup players]]\n[[Category:UEFA Euro 2012 players]]\n[[Category:2013 FIFA Confederations Cup players]]\n[[Category:2014 FIFA World Cup players]]\n[[Category:Olympic medalists in football]]\n[[Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Italy]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 2004 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:FIFA World Cup-winning players]]\n[[Category:FIFA Century Club]]\n[[Category:Italian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Italian expatriate sportspeople in the United States]]\n[[Category:Expatriate soccer players in the United States]]\n[[Category:Officers of the Order of Merit of the Italian Republic]]\n", "name_user": "2a00:23c7:3884:a00:559:565f:bc06:2494", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andrea_Pirlo"}
